# .semgrepignore
# Portal (Frontend) repo
# Semgrep skips everything listed here.
# Syntax is identical to .gitignore.

# ── Dependencies ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/

# ── Minified / bundled files ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# These are not your source — scanning them produces noisy, unfixable findings.
*.min.js
*.bundle.js
dist/
build/

# ── Vendor / third-party scripts ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Add paths to any CDN-downloaded or vendored scripts you store locally.
# e.g. js/vendor/
# js/vendor/

# ── Test files ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Uncomment if you add a test suite later.
# tests/
# *.test.js
# *.spec.js

# ── CI / tooling output ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
semgrep.sarif
eslint-results.json
